		{
			"name": "Payments",
			"description": "## Payment Flow Overview\n\n### How Payments Work:\n1. **Initiate Payment**: POST /api/payments/initiate\n   - Creates Payment record (status: Pending)\n   - Stores order data temporarily\n   - Creates SumUp checkout\n   - Returns checkout URL for customer\n\n2. **Customer Pays**: User redirected to SumUp\n   - **Success**: Redirects to `/user/payment-success?paymentId={id}`\n   - **Failure**: Redirects to `/user/payment-failed?paymentId={id}&reason={code}&message={msg}`\n\n3. **Order Creation**: Happens automatically on payment success\n   - Webhook receives payment confirmation\n   - Creates Order with OrderItems\n   - Links Payment to Order\n   - Clears pending data\n\n### Payment Retry Flow:\n- Cart is NOT cleared until payment succeeds\n- Failed payments allow retry with same items\n- User can update payment method or details\n\n### Testing (Sandbox Mode):\n- Use `/test/simulate-success` to manually complete payments\n- Use `/test/simulate-failure` to test failure scenarios\n- Poll `/checkout-status/:paymentId` for real-time status\n\n### Return URLs:\n- **Success**: `{FRONTEND_URL}/user/payment-success?paymentId={payment_id}`\n- **Failure**: `{FRONTEND_URL}/user/payment-failed?paymentId={payment_id}&reason={decline_code}&message={message}`",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Initiate Payment (Logged-in User)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{authToken}}"
							},
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"orderItems\": [\n    {\n      \"dishId\": 1,\n      \"quantity\": 2,\n      \"price\": 12.50\n    }\n  ],\n  \"totalAmount\": 25.00,\n  \"currency\": \"EUR\",\n  \"deliveryAddress\": \"Hauptstraße 123\",\n  \"area\": \"Berlin Mitte\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"10115\",\n  \"latitude\": 52.5200,\n  \"longitude\": 13.4050\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/payments/initiate",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"payments",
								"initiate"
							]
						},
						"description": "Initiate payment for logged-in user.\n\n**Returns**:\n- `checkout_url`: Redirect user here for payment\n- `paymentId`: Reference for tracking\n- `checkoutId`: SumUp checkout ID\n\n**After Payment**:\n- Success → User redirected to frontend success page\n- Failure → User redirected to frontend failure page with error details\n- Cart preserved until success to allow retry"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Initiate Payment (Guest User)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"orderItems\": [\n    {\n      \"dishId\": 1,\n      \"quantity\": 1,\n      \"price\": 10.00\n    }\n  ],\n  \"totalAmount\": 10.00,\n  \"currency\": \"EUR\",\n  \"name\": \"Guest User\",\n  \"email\": \"guest@example.com\",\n  \"phoneNo\": \"+491234567890\",\n  \"deliveryAddress\": \"Teststraße 123\",\n  \"area\": \"Berlin Mitte\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"10115\",\n  \"latitude\": 52.5200,\n  \"longitude\": 13.4050\n}"
						},
						"url": {
